des: "I went to a family event and one of my cousins brought this in. The women couldn't get enough of it. It was gone in 20 minutes!"
ins: Stir the cream cheese, mayonnaise, diced tomatoes, corn, and green onion together in a bowl. Serve immediately or chill.
